Record Class Card

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
juno.model.card.Card
Record Components:
color - The Color
value - The Value
action - The Action
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<InterfaceCard>, InterfaceCard, InterfaceCardAction, InterfaceCardColor, InterfaceCardValue
public record Card(InterfaceColor color, Integer value, InterfaceAction action) extends Record implements InterfaceCard, Comparable<InterfaceCard>
This class defines the model of the 'Uno' card. A 'Uno' card has the following attributes: - Color - Value - Action An attribute of a card can also be null, if the card type does not allow it.
